  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Digivolve] [Pulsemon]: Cost 2[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    If you have 3 or more security cards, until the end of your opponent''s turn,
    1 of your Digimon can''t have its DP reduced by your opponent''s effects and
    isn''t affected by <De-Digivolve> effects. If you have 3 or fewer, 1 of your
    Digimon gains <Blocker> and <Reboot> until the end of your opponent''s turn.'
